data.description: Here's your chance to get a spacious patio home in highly desirable Laurel Park in Concord.  Highlights include a rocking chair front porch with wrought iron rails & a large rear patio overlooking the private, fenced yard.  Inside, the home flows nicely down a wide foyer, with a formal dining room and secondary bedrooms on each side.  The kitchen features a breakfast area & granite countertops.  The kitchen is open to the great room, which features a vaulted ceiling, gas fireplace and built-in nook/bookshelves/cabinets.  Private primary suite includes a sitting area, bay window with tons of natural light, large walk-in closet and a primary bath with garden tub, shower with bench, and double sinks.  Washer, dryer and refrigerator convey.  Lawn service is included in HOA fees, so you can have plenty of time to enjoy living your best life!  Under 5 minutes to restaurants, shopping and I85.  Community amenities include 2 pools, new clubhouse, large pond, tennis courts & playground.
